{"tid":1116673,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 洪欣老公否認出軌！向法院提訴訟求清白","createTime":"2019-04-20T07:08:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-20T10:32:51.000Z","uid":48905,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3bcf91c614b84c609167d169bf0ab2d01bab3d27","tid":1116673,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T07:08:01.000Z","msg":"洪欣老公、內地男星張丹峰與經理人畢瀅同房傳「出軌」，連日來被「有系統式」爆料，張丹峰方面曾以「捕風捉影」作回應。事件發酵至今日，張丹峰終透過工作室發聲明，指已向法院提起訴訟：「通 告 <br />\n近日，針對部分網絡用戶持續傳播演員張丹峰大量不實內容，本工作室委託律師事務所就涉嫌侵權的相關內容進行取證，在歷經10天時間已全部取證並公證完畢，同時已向北京互聯網法院提起訴訟。現就有關網傳內容，本工作室在此澄清。​​​​」 <br />\n<br />\n另外，工作室又特別就5項「指控」作澄清，包括二人凌晨密會、畢瀅疑似懷孕、疑似畢瀅爆料小號、張丹峰新片被除名及張丹峰轉移財產的傳聞，均作出否定。而畢瀅的微博目前已被清空，昔日的發文及相片等均全部刪除。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4ocnJiY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4ocnJiY.png&h=dd8533bf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ae2bbb1cf2f6f54cd716884f67d670c4af0ac22e","tid":1116673,"uid":48905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T07:08:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VnPxk5V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVnPxk5V.png&h=a58d83e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b47e8dc983d02edaec44721d311afcc035fe3ceb","tid":1116673,"uid":48905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T07:09:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SaGLF56.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSaGLF56.png&h=8c252c8c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d36e8eba3a7d2570debad91620270a497664b06e","tid":1116673,"uid":48905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T07:10:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mwzxk6m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMwzxk6m.png&h=acb96826&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b353b5e029c04bf1524b24e1723dc78cbfc493f","tid":1116673,"uid":81113,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T07:10:50.000Z","msg"